data.description: Lovely 4 Bedroom/2 Bath home in established subdivision, with large backyard, covered patio and mature trees.  No carpet - flooring less than 5 years old!  Gorgeous rock fireplace in living room, kitchen with large pantry is open to breakfast, dining and living space.  Sprinkler system in yard, and backyard is large enough for a pool and has a outdoor shower for those hot, working days!  Close to schools, medical facilities and shopping.  Make an appointment to view today!
